{"data":[{"date":"01:49 17/06","title":"B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, Sampaoli v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \"t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3\" Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/bi-iceland-cam-chan-sampaoli-van-dat-niem-tin-vao-toi-do-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sampaoli k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Messi s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 d\u00f9 si\u00eau sao 30 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean m\u1ee9c th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda.</h2><h2>Th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Messi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Maxi Meza b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u00e3 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Argentina chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Messi l\u1ea1i s\u00fat qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hannes Halldorsson tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t 11 m\u00e9t. Trong 30 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\" target=\"_blank\">Argentina vs Iceland</span>, M10 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1eeda sai nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, Sampaoli v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, Sampaoli v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/bi-iceland-cam-chan-sampaoli-van-dat-niem-tin-vao-toi-do-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Messi ch\u01a1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u1ed5i h\u1ed3i c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Messi t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c. Tuy v\u1eady, HLV Sampaoli tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Messi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 b\u1edfi v\u00ec Iceland ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Messi h\u1ebft m\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Argentina. T\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Messi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sampaoli ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland nh\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00e0 Sampaoli ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Argentina \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao v\u00e0 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Iceland \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 nhanh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong hi\u1ec7p hai. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 Iceland ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1i l\u1ec7ch tr\u00e1i. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 kh\u00e2u lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng pha di chuy\u1ec3n x\u1ed9c th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u1ea3 penalty cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Iceland (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018):</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Argentina-1-1-Iceland.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Iceland:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-argentina-vs-iceland-khi-messi-nem-3-diem-ra-duong-421-188661.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland: Khi Messi n\u00e9m 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-iceland-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-messi-tren-cham-11m-421-188669.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iceland ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 Messi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"251","checkdouble":"188666"},{"date":"00:35 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-phap-21-australia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng C VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 VCK World Cup th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n (th\u1eafng 2, thua 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal (0-1) n\u0103m 2002.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Australia \u0111\u00e3 thua 4 trong 5 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2006.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Pogba-cung-dong-doi-Phap-an-mung-ban-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 1 trong s\u1ed1 7 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CH Ireland h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 4 pha c\u1ee9u thua c\u1ee7a Mat Ryan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi sau 8 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Australia th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch nhau c\u00f3 4 ph\u00fat 7 gi\u00e2y, qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Senegal vs Uruguay n\u0103m 2002 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong th\u1eddi gian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 18 tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 Antoine Griezmann ghi b\u00e0n (th\u1eafng 16, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- \u0110\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia (24 tu\u1ed5i 196 ng\u00e0y) l\u00e0 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7 n\u0103m 1930 v\u1edbi Chile.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Daniel Arzani \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup cho \u0110T Australia (19 tu\u1ed5i 163 ng\u00e0y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sam-vai-nguoi-hung-ngay-ra-quan-pogba-nhan-toi-tap-loi-khen-421-188659.html\">S\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Pogba nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi t\u1ea5p l\u1eddi khen</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gianh-chien-thang-vat-va-griezmann-noi-gi-421-188656.html\">Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, Griezmann n\u00f3i g\u00ec</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018-461-188652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-phap-vs-australia-bang-c-hom-nay-421-188645.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p vs Australia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-australia-bang-c-463-188624.html\">Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia (KT): Si\u00eau sao l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, Ph\u00e1p ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"250","checkdouble":"188667"},{"date":"02:46 17/06","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iceland ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 Messi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/thor.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Man Utd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed5ng quan t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Paul Pogba v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Ph\u00e1p kh\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ebd m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u201cqu\u00e2n xanh\u201d Australia trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i may m\u1eafn, khi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong t\u01b0 t\u1ebf v\u1edbi v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i th\u00f2 ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Aziz Behich t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mathew Ryan bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/mourinho-doi-tuoc-ban-thang-cua-tro-cung-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh cho Pogba nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-australia-bang-c-463-188624.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</span>:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTheo t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u00ednh cho Pogba, \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u00f4ng lao c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p d\u1eabn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n b\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do Griezmann, Mbappe v\u00e0 Dembele. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin ch\u01a1i m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n, m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n, thay v\u00ec h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf pressing gi\u00fap Australia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ea7u xu\u00f4i \u0111u\u00f4i l\u1ecdt m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u1eefng tin h\u01a1n tr\u00ean ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t. Th\u1ee9 n\u0103m n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Peru trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Highlights tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Phap-2-1-Australia.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"249","checkdouble":"188669"},{"date":"02:09 17/06","title":"Messi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/messi-nhan-loi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Messi m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau khi Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a cay \u0111\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Argentina b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi Iceland. Sergio Aguero \u0111\u01b0a La Albiceleste v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Alfred Finnbogason \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Iceland \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup ch\u1ec9 4 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede hi\u1ec7p hai, Messi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Argentina gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Halldorsson. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Messi c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 c\u00fa s\u00fat m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/messi-nhan-loi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Messi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Argentina \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c C\u0110V kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc tr\u1eafng xanh m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cH\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Iceland qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 khoan th\u1ee7ng. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00f9i s\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady. Qu\u1ea3 penalty khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3i xin l\u1ed7i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u00ean l\u00ean v\u00ec k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Ch\u00fang ta x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9. Nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>Messi \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<p>Messi c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 duy\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t penalty. Hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 4/7 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho CLB c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 Messi t\u1ecf ra bi quan. Trong ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, M10 c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bang-d-world-cup-2018-can-than-day-argentina-462-187893.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</span> g\u1eb7p Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi Iceland. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/bi-iceland-cam-chan-sampaoli-van-dat-niem-tin-vao-toi-do-messi-469-188666.html\">B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, Sampaoli v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-iceland-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-messi-tren-cham-11m-421-188669.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iceland ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 Messi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"248","checkdouble":"188670"},{"date":"02:48 17/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Nigeria tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/ket-qua-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Nigeria tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 02h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c Croatia vs Nigeria: 2-0<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Ghi b\u00e0n: </strong>Etebo (32', ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi), Modric (70')<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/H1-Croatia-vs-Nigeria.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Croatia-2-0-Nigeria.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Argentina b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Croatia vs Nigeria \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh l\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u1eadc. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn ngay trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 32, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc ca-ro \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn, xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u00e3 bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh ch\u1ea1m ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Etebo v\u00e0 bay v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nigeria. M\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng may m\u1eafn do \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Croatia n\u1eafm ch\u00fat l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban mo ty so trong tran Croatia vs Nigeria\" title=\"B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/etbo.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nigeria</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Croatia v\u1eabn n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, trong khi Nigeria t\u1eadp trung ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn, Luka Modric n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 \u1edf ph\u00fat 70 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Nigeria m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Ekong trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i, khi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh ch\u1ecbu qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i c\u00e3i.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban thang cua Modric Croatia vs Nigeria\" title=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Modric Croatia vs Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/modric.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Modric trong tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nigeria 2-0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, trong khi Nigeria b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca-ro s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Argentina, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh sau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"247","checkdouble":"188671"},{"date":"03:13 17/06","title":"Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/mourinho-doi-tuoc-ban-thang-cua-tro-cung-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Man Utd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed5ng quan t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Paul Pogba v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Ph\u00e1p kh\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ebd m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u201cqu\u00e2n xanh\u201d Australia trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i may m\u1eafn, khi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong t\u01b0 t\u1ebf v\u1edbi v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i th\u00f2 ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Aziz Behich t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mathew Ryan bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/mourinho-doi-tuoc-ban-thang-cua-tro-cung-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh cho Pogba nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-australia-bang-c-463-188624.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</span>:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTheo t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u00ednh cho Pogba, \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u00f4ng lao c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p d\u1eabn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n b\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do Griezmann, Mbappe v\u00e0 Dembele. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin ch\u01a1i m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n, m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n, thay v\u00ec h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf pressing gi\u00fap Australia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ea7u xu\u00f4i \u0111u\u00f4i l\u1ecdt m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u1eefng tin h\u01a1n tr\u00ean ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t. Th\u1ee9 n\u0103m n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Peru trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Highlights tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Phap-2-1-Australia.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"246","checkdouble":"188673"},{"date":"02:42 17/06","title":"Aguero b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi sau pha s\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1ee3t pen th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/aguero-bao-ve-messi-sau-pha-sut-truot-pen-tham-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sergio Aguero \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi sau khi c\u00fa s\u00fat penalty h\u1ecfng \u0103n c\u1ee7a M10 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Argentina b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ngay trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Aguero b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aguero l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Argentina v\u1edbi Iceland t\u1ea1i Moscow h\u00f4m qua. Tuy v\u1eady, pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Aguero kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Argentina chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi Finnbogason \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Iceland ch\u1ec9 \u00edt ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Argentina \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 Messi. Si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 11 c\u00fa s\u00fat m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Argentina t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aguero b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi sau pha s\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1ee3t pen th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Aguero b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi sau pha s\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1ee3t pen th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Aguero-bao-ve-Messi-sau-pha-sut-truot-pen-tham-hoa-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Aguero b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u00f3a nh\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng lao c\u1ee7a Messi. Ch\u00ednh c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Ecuador \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn Nga. V\u00e0 Aguero \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMessi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. H\u00f4m nay, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u1edf b\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean lu\u00f4n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 Argentina mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Argentina g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Iceland</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Javier Mascherano, s\u1edf d\u0129 Argentina g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u00e0 v\u00ec Iceland \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c C\u0110V. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed5 v\u0169 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u1edf b\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Argentina-1-1-Iceland.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/bi-iceland-cam-chan-sampaoli-van-dat-niem-tin-vao-toi-do-messi-469-188666.html\">B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, Sampaoli v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-iceland-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-messi-tren-cham-11m-421-188669.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iceland ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 Messi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"245","checkdouble":"188674"},{"date":"04:01 17/06","title":"Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Iceland m\u00e3n nguy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/thuyen-truong-iceland-man-nguyen-voi-1-diem-lich-su-truoc-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Argentina, HLV Hallgrimsson t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nIceland xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, tuy nhi\u00ean Iceland v\u1eabn l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Argentina, v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-1 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f2n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hannes Haldorsson c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Leo Messi. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a do c\u00f4ng Alfred Finnbogason, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iceland \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson c\u1ee7a Iceland cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i, khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hallgrimsson t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Iceland\" title=\"Heimir Hallgrimsson Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/thuyen-truong-iceland-man-nguyen-voi-1-diem-lich-su-truoc-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Hallgrimsson t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, Argentina s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ec3 gi\u1edbi. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Argentina \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n ra theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a h\u00f4m nay s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Iceland cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng Heimir Hallgrimsson v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nha s\u0129, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia b\u00e1n th\u1eddi gian. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Hannes Haldorsson &ndash; th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 qu\u1ea3 penalty c\u1ee7a Messi c\u0169ng v\u1eady, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n phim. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, HLV Hallgrimsson t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Iceland s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Nigeria v\u00e0 Croatia, v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Argentina 1-1 Iceland\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina 1-1 Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Thong-so-Argentina-vs-Iceland.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina 1-1 Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Argentina-1-1-Iceland.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-iceland-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-messi-tren-cham-11m-421-188669.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/thor.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-iceland-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-messi-tren-cham-11m-421-188669.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iceland ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 Messi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</span><br>\r\nHannes Thor Halldorsson cho bi\u1ebft anh \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-thong-ke-noi-len-su-tham-hai-cua-messi-so-voi-ronaldo-421-188663.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/day-thong-ke-noi-len-su-tham-hai-cua-messi-so-voi-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-thong-ke-noi-len-su-tham-hai-cua-messi-so-voi-ronaldo-421-188663.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Messi so v\u1edbi Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Argentina v\u00e0 Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1, khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t Iceland l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tham d\u1ef1 World Cup.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"244","checkdouble":"188675"},{"date":"02:53 17/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-0 Nigeria (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng T\u1eed th\u1ea7n. </h2><strong>B\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n VTV</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nCroatia: Subasic; Vrsaljko, Lovren, Vida, Strinic; Perisic, Modric, Rakitic, Rebic; Kramaric, Mandzukic<br>\r\nNigeria: Uzoho; Shehu, Troost-Ekong, Balogun; Idowu, Ndidi, Etebo, Moses, Mikel; Iwobi, Ighalo <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"243","checkdouble":"188676"},{"date":"03:18 17/06","title":"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/17/3-ly-do-khien-argentina-bi-iceland-cam-chan-ngay-ra-quan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Argentina \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed5i Iceland d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a La Albiceleste trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>\u00c1p \u0111\u1ea3o nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/031444-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1eeda tr\u00ean. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 78% th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, Argentina tung ra 752 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1t g\u1ea7n 90%. La Albiceleste s\u00fat 27 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 27 c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u00f3, c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 6 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ecb c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 b\u1edfi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Halldorsson c\u1ee7a Iceland. 20 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n n\u00e0o qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup nh\u01b0 Argentina, nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 HLV Jorge Sampaoli s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u00eam kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Lo\u1ea1i Paulo Dybala kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dybala\" title=\"Dybala\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/180214-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u00f3 Dybala, Argentina ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i kh\u00e1 t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o khi lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ng\u00f4i sao Paulo Dybala kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iceland. V\u00e0 canh b\u1ea1c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Sampaoli ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Argentina \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua thi\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n \u0111i s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Dybala tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMaximiliano Meza l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Dybala s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Iceland kh\u00f3 th\u1edf h\u01a1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 26 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSampaoli c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Dybala b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Messi v\u00e0 Aguero \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo g\u1eb7p Croatia. Thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 Dybala th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Messi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi\" title=\"Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Aguero-bao-ve-Messi-sau-pha-sut-truot-pen-tham-hoa-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Messi l\u00e0 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 khi\u1ebfn Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Ronaldo t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nhu\u1ed1m m\u00e0u si\u00eau sao cho B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00eam qua, m\u1ecdi \u00e1nh m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o Messi. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Barcelona s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi h\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e1p th\u1ecfa \u0111\u00e1ng. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0 Iceland, Messi c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i l\u1eddi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Ronaldo b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Messi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o. \u1ea2o thu\u1eadt gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra 9 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng r\u00ea b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 tung ra 11 c\u00fa s\u00fat (3 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch). Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p Messi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Messi khi anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 64. Khi \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n sau khi Meza b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u0129nh tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Halldorsson \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Messi v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u1ede nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat ti\u1ebfp theo, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 v\u1ebb ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Argentina 1-1 Iceland (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018) </strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Argentina-1-1-Iceland.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Iceland:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/bi-iceland-cam-chan-sampaoli-van-dat-niem-tin-vao-toi-do-messi-469-188666.html\">B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, Sampaoli v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-iceland-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-messi-tren-cham-11m-421-188669.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iceland ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 Messi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"242","checkdouble":"188677"},{"date":"18:29 16/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhung-nhan-dinh-peru-vs-dan-mach-va-du-doan-peru-vs-dan-mach.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Croatia vs Nigeria: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 02h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Croatia vs Nigeria: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 02h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-463-188655.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP CROATIA VS NIGERIA</strong></u></span></span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"241","checkdouble":"188650"},{"date":"18:25 16/06","title":"T\u1ea3n m\u1ea1n World Cup: T\u1eeb tr\u1eadn Maroc 0-1 Iran ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/tan-man-world-cup-tu-tran-maroc-01-iran-nghi-ve-bong-da-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn b\u1ecb \u00e9p s\u00e2n to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, \u0110T Iran v\u1eabn may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u01a1n ra th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Iran may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf World Cup</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/6, \u0110T Iran c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 5 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong 4 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0110T Iran ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua 8, h\u00f2a 3 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a Iran tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n M\u1ef9 \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Ph\u00e1p.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">20 n\u0103m cho nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eadn may c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Iran khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ch\u01a1i l\u00e9p v\u1ebf to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma-r\u1ed1c song chung cu\u1ed9c, Iran l\u1ea1i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&nbsp;<strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/maroc-vs-iran-bang-b-463-188560.html\" target=\"_blank\">1-0</span>&nbsp;</strong>v\u1edbi m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 t\u1eeb tr\u00ean tr\u1eddi r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Maroc, Aziz Bouhaddouz \u0111\u1ed1t l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+5.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1eeb tr\u1eadn Maroc 0-1 \u0110T Iran ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u1eeb tr\u1eadn Maroc 0-1 \u0110T Iran ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Tu-tran-Maroc-0-1-DT-Iran-nghi-ve-bong-da-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Iran may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Iran \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Maroc h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng. Iran g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tri\u1ec3n khai c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 y\u1ebfu \u1edbt, khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Beiranvand ph\u1ea3i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u Phi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, \u0110T Maroc li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec1m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Iran. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 l\u0103n x\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng 3 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c1 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Iran m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u00fd ngh\u0129a. 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i Brazil, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Iran, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Australia ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00fang b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 12 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba kh\u00e1c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. D\u1eabu sao th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Carlos Queiroz c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, d\u00f9 v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Iran, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Australia v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ma-roc-truoc-iran-421-188588.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ma-roc-truoc-iran.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ma-roc-truoc-iran-421-188588.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Ma R\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</span><br>\r\nMa R\u1ed1c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Iran nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran b\u1ea3ng B...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t xa World Cup<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 nh\u01b0 Iran tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Maroc m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng thay v\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh d\u1ef1 Wolrd Cup trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Iran, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo DT Viet Nam\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/park-hang-seo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Iran c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m sau, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0110T Iran c\u1ee7a HLV Carlos Queiroz, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i: &ldquo;7 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa, n\u1ebfu Iran mang to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch l\u1eafm!&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. N\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 v\u1eeba tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb v\u1edbi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iran t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 9X. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Iran l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 20, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sardar Azmoun c\u00f2n b\u1eb1ng tu\u1ed5i C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Iran \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb, kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, d\u00f9 Iran c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e2ng cao y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i chung khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"240","checkdouble":"188651"},{"date":"18:56 16/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, Les Bleus v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, hai b\u00ean thi nhau ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a VAR.</h2><strong>B\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n VTV</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p:</strong> Lloris, Pavard, Varane, Umtiti, Hernandez, Kante, Pogba, Tolisso, Mbappe, Griezmann, Dembele<br>\r\n<strong>Australia:</strong> Ryan; Risdon, Milligan, Sainsbury, Behich; Jedinak, Mooy; Kruse, Leckie, Rogic; Nabbout <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"239","checkdouble":"188652"},{"date":"20:23 16/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Croatia vs Nigeria 02h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Croatia vs Nigeria: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 02h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Croatia vs Nigeria: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 02h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-463-188655.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP CROATIA VS NIGERIA</strong></u></span></span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"238","checkdouble":"188655"},{"date":"21:03 16/06","title":"Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, Griezmann n\u00f3i g\u00ec","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/gianh-chien-thang-vat-va-griezmann-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Dider Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia.\r\n</h2><h2>Griezmann kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfm hoi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR, do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Umtiti, gi\u00fap Australia c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Paul Pogba may m\u1eafn ghi b\u00e0n, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Atletico Madrid t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Griezmann cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn sau. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia\" title=\"Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/gianh-chien-thang-vat-va-griezmann-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft l\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng, v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhau. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois &ndash; ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c. Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ghi b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng tai, m\u0169i hay ch\u00e2n, kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Pogba v\u00e0 Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-australia-bang-c-463-188624.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</span>, &ldquo;t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3&rdquo; Samuel Umtiti c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay. Trung v\u1ec7 Barca c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eeda sai gi\u00fap m\u00ecnh, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Phap 2-1 Australia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Phap-2--Australia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"font-size: 12px; width: 300px; height: 220px;\" alt=\"\"></h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018-461-188652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018-461-188652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, Les Bleus v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-phap-vs-australia-bang-c-hom-nay-421-188645.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/ket-qua-phap-vs-australia-bang-c-hom-nay.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-phap-vs-australia-bang-c-hom-nay-421-188645.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p vs Australia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p vs Australia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"237","checkdouble":"188656"}]}